name: ExportOptionsPhotoshop
shortdesc: Options which may be supplied when exporting a document as a Photoshop file.

property.name: imageColorSpace
property.shortdesc: The color space of the exported file.

property.name: resolution
property.shortdesc: The resolution of the exported file.

property.name: antiAliasing
property.shortdesc: Should the resulting image be antialiased.

property.name: editableText
property.shortdesc: Export text objects as editable text layers.

property.name: embedICCProfile
property.shortdesc: Embed an ICC profile when exporting.

property.name: warnings
property.shortdesc: Should a warning dialog be displayed because of conflicts in the export settings.

property.name: maximumEditability
property.shortdesc: Preserve as much of the original document's structure as possible when exporting.

property.name: saveMultipleArtboards
property.shortdesc: All the artboards or range of the artboards will be exported.

property.name: artboardRange
property.shortdesc: If SaveMultipleArtboards is true,this will be considered for multi-asset extraction which specifies artboard range.Empty string will extracts all the artboards.Default is empty string.
